{"tid":1298462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「要改姓賴」足球上帝美斯輸波後/抗壓時賴三賴四精華一覽（含近年剪報精華）","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:32:29.000Z","uid":5006,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b87a4119ad5d302e0cd9863a77663a768fa76d9b","tid":1298462,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"屌，上網一搵，原來國家隊球會<span style=\"color: red;\">教練隊友球證足證草地</span>都比佢屌/賴過，呀小花真係惡過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. <strong>賴<span style=\"color: red;\">教練</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">隊友</span>問題：</strong><br />\n<strong>傳遷怒高層兼隊友 美斯嬲爆！(2018)</strong><br />\n西班牙傳媒報道，巴塞隆拿在歐聯8強滑鐵盧出局後，靈魂美斯對主帥華維迪的調兵遣將甚為不滿，更有報道指美斯<span style=\"color: red;\">遷怒於6名隊友</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=21058830902&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D21058830902%26refer%3Dshare&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=93716f0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D21058830902%26refer%3Dshare&h=7c340334\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=21058830902&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美斯世界盃當眾怒斥阿根廷教練(2018)</strong><br />\n馬斯查蘭奴和美斯帶頭向桑保利發難，<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯甚至表示</span>：「我們不知道你的想法是什麼，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們不再信任你了</span>，我們想要有自己的觀點。」<br />\n對此桑保利非常驚訝：「什麼觀點？」美斯和馬斯查蘭奴回答說：「各方面的觀點。」桑保利聽到球員這麼說顯得難以置信：「那你們來組建球隊，來指導訓練是不是？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180720/4/19/2/%E9%A9%9A%E6%9B%9D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E7%A7%98%E8%81%9E-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E7%95%B6%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%A5%E8%B2%AC%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4-9049352.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F4%2F19%2F2%2F%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%259B%259D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259B%2583%25E7%25A7%2598%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B7%25B4-9049352.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=17ab4efa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180720/4/19/2/%E9%A9%9A%E6%9B%9D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E7%A7%98%E8%81%9E-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E7%95%B6%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%A5%E8%B2%AC%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4-9049352.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>賴<span style=\"color: red;\">足總</span>問題：<br />\n阿根廷出局-美斯爆粗轟裁判-斥var形同虛設(2019)</strong><br />\n「南美足協可以做一些跟進。不過，他們肯定不會去做，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">他們已經被巴西控制</span>。」(美斯, 2019)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/347666/美洲國家盃2019-阿根廷出局-美斯爆粗轟裁判-斥var形同虛設\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F347666%2F%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%832019-%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%B1%80-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E7%88%86%E7%B2%97%E8%BD%9F%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4-%E6%96%A5var%E5%BD%A2%E5%90%8C%E8%99%9B%E8%A8%AD&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=8ddd3e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/347666/美洲國家盃2019-阿根廷出局-美斯爆粗轟裁判-斥var形同虛設</a><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>賴<span style=\"color: red;\">球證</span>問題：<br />\n美斯被逐怒批球證腐敗(2019)</strong><br />\n「這些<span style=\"color: red;\">球證很多都是腐敗的</span>，我們帶著他們不讓己隊打入決賽的感覺離開巴西。」(美斯. 2019)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/體育/阿根廷獲美洲盃季軍-美斯被逐怒批球證腐敗-179474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2%E7%9B%83%E5%AD%A3%E8%BB%8D-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%90%E6%80%92%E6%89%B9%E7%90%83%E8%AD%89%E8%85%90%E6%95%97-179474&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=ff875477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/體育/阿根廷獲美洲盃季軍-美斯被逐怒批球證腐敗-179474</a><br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>怒屌<span style=\"color: red;\">記者</span>：<br />\n美斯帶領阿根廷國家隊杯葛傳媒(2016)</strong><br />\n「我們決定<span style=\"color: red;\">不再與傳媒交流</span>。我們受到很多指責，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">不獲尊重</span>，但我們從沒有講任何說話。抱歉我們只有作出這個決定，別無其他選擇。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/423332-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%98%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%9A%8A%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fmacau%2Farticle%2F423332-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%2591%259B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=ea3c0fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/423332-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%98%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%9A%8A%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92</a><br />\n<br />\n5. <strong>賴<span style=\"color: red;\">草地</span>問題：</strong><br />\n<strong>賴地「彈」？美斯轟美洲盃草地質素（2019）</strong><br />\n「我們在3個不同地方（新水源球場、明尼路球場及甘美奧球場）進行過比賽，但它們的狀況均很糟糕。當<span style=\"color: red;\">球在草地上滾動時，常常都會反彈</span>，因此必須花更多力氣才能阻止這情況發生，比賽的難度亦大大提升。」美斯（Lionel Messi）接受西班牙《馬卡報》訪問時說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26007370154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D26007370154&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=21f71b11\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26007370154</a><br />\n<br />\n呀美斯你不如唔好叫做美斯啦，賴三賴四咁叻，直接改名做賴屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來班花迷賴到一地，係學埋晒佢地偶像既絕技，上樑不正下樑歪，真係明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea508f2496